      "rationale": "Titanium alloy components modeled as bilinear elastic-plastic with isotropic hardening, consistent with Ti-6Al-4V stress-strain data. Large-deformation kinematics activated given >5% strain at failure. Contact formulated with augmented Lagrangian method. Model form consistent with published FDA guidance and prior F1717 FEA literature."
