      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single test condition (ambient temperature, quasi-static 5 mm/min crosshead speed) per ASTM F1717. Only one loading configuration tested (compression-bending at 5-degree offset). This factor is below required level; the gap is acknowledged and accepted given that F1717 is the regulatory standard and clinical loading envelope is well-characterized for this device class."
