    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) is below required level (achieved 2, required 3) due to single test condition; this gap is accepted given that ASTM F1717 is the applicable regulatory standard and the single loading condition is representative of the COU. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, <10% difference). The credibility assessment supports the Accepted decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA framework.",
